body: "GH-598. ensurePmGitignore (GH-514/pm-hous lineage) writes the managed runtime/cache ignore block with the tracker root hardcoded to .agents/pm/ instead of the resolved root. Workspaces using --pm-path/PM_PATH/custom roots commit runtime caches → guaranteed index churn and merge conflicts for multi-agent branches. Fix: render the resolved root into the fenced block, keep idempotency; regression test for custom-root init."
